songs.title: Rectifiya
songs.lyrics:
who rectifying me? 
  
 i can never quite figure out 
 how to walk before i run 
 i will never reel in my shine, wear a shade 
 these niggas on my back like white on rice 
 claiming they get healing from my energy 
 but baby, i need them to reciprocate 
  
 see, i dedicate my life to this 
 and i predicate my consciousness and state of well being 
 on my own feelings 
 
 who rectifying me?
